com.ibm.cloud.sdk.core.security

Interface Authenticator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicAuthenticator, BearerTokenAuthenticator, CloudPakForDataAuthenticator, CloudPakForDataServiceAuthenticator, CloudPakForDataServiceInstanceAuthenticator, ContainerAuthenticator, IamAuthenticator, IamRequestBasedAuthenticator, NoAuthAuthenticator, TokenRequestBasedAuthenticator, VpcInstanceAuthenticator

    public interface Authenticator
    This interface defines the common methods and constants associated with an Authenticator implementation.
